---
title: Burrito-Style Tex-Mex Beef Tacos with Pico de Gallo & Red Pepper Crema
description: Craving tacos? Daydreaming about burritos? Then let’s taco ‘bout what’s for dinner! Our chefs put together a Tex-Mex-inspired taco-burrito hybrid that’s sure to satisfy. There’s ground turkey and onion simmered with Mexican-style spices, pico de gallo, red pepper crema, and jasmine rice, all piled into steamy-soft tortillas. The best part? You’ll be savoring these beauties in only 20 minutes!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65007c7a5d7b00d769c55fcc-ebd7238d.jpeg
